ids\ncontained within the switchbacks. In the Appendix, we examine a series of\nsetups with different switchback configurations and parameters, which broaden\nthe scope of our study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 17:12:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
