 outflows with the amount of time elapsed since their\nacceleration (probably driven by shocks) as a consequence of the cooling that\noccurred during the pPN phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 19:01:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
