 automated verification tool for Ethereum smart contracts written in\nthe Vyper language, and demonstrated its effectiveness in succinctly capturing\nand verifying strong correctness guarantees for real-world contracts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 22:36:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2021 11:06:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-10"}
