r compared to any other reported aptamer-based\nmethods for mycotoxin detection. The sensors hold comparable performance when\noperated in real-time within a complex matrix of wine without additional\ntime-consuming pre-treatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2021 14:18:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 03:55:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2021 17:36:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-14"}
