eral,\nour approach to radiation reaction for eccentric inspirals should be seen as a\nfirst step toward EOB modelization of extreme-mass-ratio-inspirals waveforms\nfor LISA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2021 14:30:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 12:55:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Dec 2021 08:39:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 10:32:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-31"}
